      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "\ud83c\udf1f Rare Find Alert! Looking for a car that feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor? This stunning vehicle is in absolutely mint condition \u2014 everything is in exceptional shape, from the gleaming exterior to the spotless interior and the smooth, responsive drive. This is truly a turn-key, worry-free purchase with no surprises waiting for you. Whether you're a car enthusiast seeking perfection or simply want the very best, this is the one you've been waiting for. Come see it in person \u2014 you won't be disappointed!",
