    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in fair condition, and we want to give you a complete and honest picture before you make your decision. The exterior shows noticeable wear \u2014 expect visible scratches, some paint fading, and minor dents consistent with everyday use over the years. The interior is functional but shows its age, with worn upholstery, some scuffs on the trim, and general signs of regular use. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, though we recommend a pre-purchase inspection as there may be items that need attention in the near term. This is a practical, budget-friendly option for a buyer who understands they're getting a vehicle that will require some investment of time or money to bring up to a higher standard \u2014 priced accordingly to reflect that reality.",
      "price": 19500.0,
