    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed honestly as a mint-condition car, representing the finest example of a used vehicle you are likely to find on the market. The exterior is virtually flawless \u2014 the paint retains a deep, showroom-quality shine with absolutely no scratches, chips, or blemishes of any kind. Every body panel is perfectly aligned, and the chrome and trim pieces are immaculate. The interior is equally impressive, with pristine upholstery, spotless carpeting, and a dashboard free of any cracks, fading, or wear. All electronic systems, controls, and infotainment features function perfectly. Under the hood, the engine is clean, well-maintained, and performs with full power and responsiveness. Service records are complete and up to date, reflecting meticulous ownership. The tires are in excellent condition with substantial tread remaining. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a used vehicle that truly looks and drives like new \u2014 ideal for the buyer who refuses to compromise on quality.",
      "price": 47000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
