      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Pristine, Flawless & Ready to Impress \u2013 A True Mint-Condition Treasure! \ud83d\ude97\n\nThis vehicle is as close to perfect as you'll find on the used market \u2014 and we mean that! It has been exceptionally maintained, and every detail reflects the care it has received. The exterior shines without a blemish, the interior looks and smells fresh, and the mechanical components perform like the day it rolled off the lot. This is genuinely a rare opportunity to own a used car that feels brand new. If you've been searching for something you can be truly proud of, look no further \u2014 this one is the real deal!",
      "price": 46000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in truly exceptional, mint condition \u2014 and we mean that sincerely. From the moment you lay eyes on it, you'll notice the exterior is flawless: the paint finish gleams with a deep, showroom-quality shine, completely free of scratches, chips, swirl marks, or blemishes of any kind. Every panel is straight and true, the trim is pristine, and the glass is crystal clear without a single chip or crack. Step inside and you'll find an interior that looks and smells as though it just rolled off the lot \u2014 the upholstery is spotless, all surfaces are unmarked, and every feature, button, and control functions exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine is clean, well-maintained, and runs with smooth, confident power. The tires have excellent tread depth remaining, and the brakes, suspension, and all mechanical systems are in top working order. This is a rare opportunity to purchase a vehicle that has been exceptionally well cared for throughout its life. A buyer can expect to drive this car with complete confidence from day one.",
      "price": 46000.0,
